intro: Every jump is a step closer to the top!
description:
Start from scratch and get to the top in ONLY Sky Parkour: Island UP! A game where every jump counts.
It doesn't matter how many times you fall - it matters how many times you get back up again. Control your movement, overcome obstacles and move up, one step at a time.
You play as a brave girl who decided to conquer the sky. Unlock new images and skins to pass the way in your own style - from cute outfits to bright and daring images.
Checkpoints will help you record success, but the rest is only in your hands.
Are you ready to prove you can make it to the end?
